WEBVTT

00:00:00.467 --> 00:00:04.003
Sometimes when an Employee is denied promotion due to lack of

00:00:04.070 --> 00:00:07.340
work or funds, he or she will perform the work of a

00:00:07.407 --> 00:00:10.510
higher-graded position on a temporary basis.

00:00:10.577 --> 00:00:16.116
Per Article 25 and VA policy, if an employee temporarily performs

00:00:16.182 --> 00:00:19.319
the work of the higher-graded position for the required amount

00:00:19.386 --> 00:00:23.790
of time to be eligible, he or she will be temporarily promoted

00:00:23.857 --> 00:00:25.658
and paid appropriately.


